name: IAM-01_4pt
description: v4w.enko - "IAM-01_4pt" [Intermediate Algorithmic Multicomponent - 01_4pt]  is an abstraction which connects intermediate cross-pattern`s instructions to demonstrate the multicomponent relationship of various geometric algorithms. Abstraction 01_4pt is dedicated to the artistic interpretation of the "Metaball", "Voronoi diagram" and "Delaunay triangulation". Standard patterns whose settings are linked to each other in specific way to draw the algorithmic abstract artwork. The artwork shows the energy of some abstract processes in relationship of linked algorithms. Four charged points are  transforming the space around and are forming the whole image of the new geometric canvas. Packed as GIF. 1024*1024px / 141 frames.
